-chronicles_26_6","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":6,"text":"And to Samaias his son were born the sons of his first-born, chiefs over the house of their father, for they were mighty.","searchKeywords":["and","samaias","his","son","were","born","the","sons","first","chiefs","over","house","their","father","for","they","mighty"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_7","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":7,"text":"The sons of Samai; Othni, and Raphael, and Obed, and Elzabath, and Achiud, mighty men, Heliu, and Sabachia, and Isbacom.","searchKeywords":["the","sons","samai","othni","and","raphael","obed","elzabath","achiud","mighty","men","heliu","sabachia","isbacom"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_8","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":8,"text":"All of the sons of Abdedom, they and their sons and their brethren, doing mightily in service: in all sixty-two to Abdedom.","searchKeywords":["all","the","sons","abdedom","they","and","their","brethren","doing","mightily","service","sixty","two"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_9","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":9,"text":"And Mosellemia eighteen sons and brethren, mighty men.","searchKeywords":["and","mosellemia","eighteen","sons","brethren","mighty","men"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_10","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":10,"text":"And to Osa of the sons of Merari sons, keeping the dominion; though he was not the first-born, yet his father made him chief of the second division.","searchKeywords":["and","osa","the","sons","merari","keeping","dominion","though","was","not","first","born","yet","his","father","made","him","chief","second","division"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_11","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":11,"text":"Chelcias the second, Tablai the third, Zacharias the fourth: all these the sons and brethren of Osa, thirteen.","searchKeywords":["chelcias","the","second","tablai","third","zacharias","fourth","all","these","sons","and","brethren","osa","thirteen"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_12","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":12,"text":"To these the divisions of the gates, to the chiefs of the mighty men the daily courses, even their brethren, to minister in the house of the Lord.","searchKeywords":["these","the","divisions","gates","chiefs","mighty","men","daily","courses","even","their","brethren","minister","house","lord"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_13","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":13,"text":"And they cast lots for the small as well as for the great, for the several gates, according to their families.","searchKeywords":["and","they","cast","lots","for","the","small","well","great","several","gates","according","their","families"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_14","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":26,"verse":14,"text":"And the lot of the east gates fell to Selemias, and Zacharias: the sons of Soaz cast lots for Melchias, and the lot came out northward.","searchKeywords":["and","the","lot","east","gates","fell","selemias","zacharias","sons","soaz","cast","lots","for","melchias","came","out","northward"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_26_15","translationId"